snippet.title: SMASH BROS TEMPLE in BANJO KAZOOIE (N64 Mod)
snippet.description:
#BanjoKazooie #SuperSmashBros #Nintendo64 
"Banjo Kazooie - Smash Bros TEMPLE" is a 100% playable BK Mod fo N64. In it you can explore the TEMPLE stage (from Super Smash Bros. Melee) in a brand new 3D adventure.
COLLECTABLES:
- 100 Notes
- 8 Jiggies
- 2 Honeycomb pieces 

SUPPORT my Youtube channel: https://www.patreon.com/Kurko or https://www.paypal.me/KurkoMods
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/kurko_mods
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Markus_Kurko 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/Kurko_mods/

DOWNLOAD: Just drop your "Banjo-Kazooie (U) [!]" rom here https://patch.wedarobi.com/bk_smash_bros_temple

SOUNDTRACK HERE:
https://soundcloud.com/sheeshfr/sets/full-ost-banjo-kazooie-smash
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWv5ylwecdA&list=PLQGByA4uRLav0CGqPBtog1M9shMlStYqK

COMPOSER:
TWITTER: @SheeshFr
